item.dc:creator: @xx_qwertyuiop_xx xx qwertyuiop xx
item.description:
@xx_qwertyuiop_xx wrote:

Find out what variable you use.
And fix up that code, it’s ugly and redundant.

public void enterCrater() {
    if (combatLevel >= 3 && combatLevel < 85) {
        teleportToX = 2863;
        teleportToY = 9570;
    } else if (combatLevel >= 85 && combatLevel < 105) {
        teleportToX = 2464;
        teleportToY = 4782;
    } else if (combatLevel >= 105 && combatLevel <= 126) {
        teleportToX = 1894;
        teleportToY = 5333;
    }
    appearanceUpdateRequired = true;
    sM("Welcome To Bounty Hunter.");
    updateRequired = true;
}
